{"tid":585751,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[Switch/3DS機主討論區]|Direct情報整合|DS太陽戰士Amiibo|瑪網&大亂鬥中文版(79)","createTime":"2018-03-09T02:48:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-09T03:31:26.000Z","uid":66113,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5868eb0369718d83fbdf1e1daea6e30f94371e3b","tid":585751,"uid":66113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T02:48:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>本Post自二月起因不明原因遭受惡意負評 <br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">(請參考過去嘅post, 全部留言都有負評 -<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/573253/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/573253/page/1</a>)</span></span><br />\n另外有會員不時以盲反言論洗版, <br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">(例子: <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/573253/page/35\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/573253/page/35</a> &amp; <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/543453/page/40\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/543453/page/40</a>)</span></span><br />\n並選擇性無視其他巴打嘅回應<br />\n請善用「封鎖會員」功能。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\nNintendo Direct 2018/03/09 <br />\n內容重溫:<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UFBnkxuICco\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DUFBnkxuICco&d=w1FSeGkS6ex%2B3phm3q1pv%2F7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=891fca84\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UFBnkxuICco</a><br />\n<br />\n3DS:<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DXzFR1MUMAE4ef9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDXzFR1MUMAE4ef9.jpg&h=159bedce&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DXzFglZVwAAL_eH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDXzFglZVwAAL_eH.jpg&h=c82e32d4&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DXzFyMOUQAA4x7w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F