/104720_88949cfa9f0ecee78fe242072b11e2f9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F09%2F104720_88949cfa9f0ecee78fe242072b11e2f9.jpg&h=2d31000a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</div>"},{"pid":"605f467e5b93565e4ffdc3a7de097e788f8364a6","tid":585751,"uid":66113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T02:48:46.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://www.nintendo.com.hk/software/switch/img/panel_kirby_star_allies.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nintendo.com.hk%2Fsoftware%2Fswitch%2Fimg%2Fpanel_kirby_star_allies.png&h=f855c659&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>遊戲<span style=\"color: red;\">試玩版</span>已於 <span style=\"color: red;\">美/歐 eShop</span>推出, 對應<span style=\"color: red;\">中文</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DXN2e8nU0AAp6PE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDXN2e8nU0AAp6PE.jpg&h=319566b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>『星之卡比 新星同盟』TVCM1</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/4KS-ItrqBF0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F4KS-ItrqBF0&d=w1FSeGkS6ex%2B3phm3q1pv%2F7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=ddd881a2\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/4KS-ItrqBF0</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>『星之卡比 新星同盟』TVCM2</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/_ijdilSOhuI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F_ijdilSOhuI&d=w1FSeGkS6ex%2B3phm3q1pv%2F7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=0fe5c4a2\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/_ijdilSOhuI</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.nintendo.com.hk/software/switch/img/panel_zelda_hw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nintendo.com.hk%2Fsoftware%2Fswitch%2Fimg%2Fpanel_zelda_hw.png&h=fbe38a17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.nintendo.com.hk/software/switch/img/panel_zelda_21.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nintendo.com.hk%2Fsoftware%2Fswitch%2Fimg%2Fpanel_zelda_21.png&h=f36d8a95&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">『薩爾達傳說 曠野之息』宣傳影片</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jXbtGKC1CsI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DjXbtGKC1CsI&d=w1FSeGkS6ex%2B3phm3q1pv%2F7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=8553adcc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jXbtGKC1CsI</a><br />\n---------<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港eShop</span> 4月3日起 開始服務<br />\n暫時<span style=\"color: red;\">只支援兌換遊戲功能</span><br />\n需上香港任天堂官網購買遊戲兌換碼</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\">- 詳情 - </span><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.nintendo.com.hk/pressrelease/switch_eshop_20180306.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nintendo.com.hk%2Fpressrelease%2Fswitch_eshop_20180306.htm&d=w1FSeGkS6ex%2B3phm3q1pv%2F7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=ab9547ec\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nintendo.com.hk/pressrelease/switch_eshop_20180306.htm</a><br />\n----------<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">任天堂會員服務 My Nintendo 之金幣可於Switch eShop 中當作現金使用</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DXnASsWWAAAJSLc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDXnASsWWAAAJSLc.jpg&h=1ec796e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</div>"},{"pid":"d9f7a8976771af4cbcf7e5fc31f5d7ea1fcb97fe","tid":585751,"uid":6366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T02:50:34.000Z","msg":"啲圖多到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f9fe8edf5f1889074dc111fb423a01ca166bafb","tid":585751,"uid":66113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T02:51:29.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">新發售遊戲 ([ ]中為對應語言)</span></strong></span><br />\n</div><br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\"><strong>Switch:</strong></span> <br />\n3月8日 你的四騎姬教導譚<br />\n3月15日 Winning Post 8 2018<br />\n3月15日 進擊的巨人2<br />\n3月16日 星之卡比: 新星同盟 [中文]<br />\n3月22日 Zelda無雙 海拉魯全明星豪華版 [中文]<br />\n3月22日 星光樂園 All Idol Perfect Stage<br />\n3月22日 Monster Energy Supercross - The Official Videogame<br />\n3月29日 蒼の彼方のフォーリズム for Nintendo Switch<br />\n3月29日 Happy Birthdays<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>3DS:</strong></span> <br />\n3月23日 名偵探比卡超 [中文]<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: navy;\"><strong>Amiibo</strong></span>:<br />\n3月23日 超巨型名偵探比卡超Amiibo<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>iOS/Android</strong></span>: <br />\n11月22日 動物之森: Pocket Camp 免費 [日/英文]<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>常見問題</strong></span></span></div><br />\n <br />\nQ: 駁上電視玩 畫面會定格/疾, 但係手提mode又無事?<br />\nA: 有批機出事, 請致電香港任天堂安排更換<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.nintendo.com.hk/switch/repair.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nintendo.com.hk%2Fswitch%2Frepair.html&d=w1FSeGkS6ex%2B3phm3q1pv%2F7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=eb7e7157\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nintendo.com.hk/switch/repair.html</a><br />\n <br />\nQ: 孖車/炸彈人/ARMS/Splatoon2等網絡對戰遊戲online玩唔到?<br />\nA: 港服未開, 去<a href=\"https://accounts.nintendo.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faccounts.nintendo.com&d=w1FSeGkS6ex%2B3phm3q1pv%2F7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=a35141fb\" target=\"_blank\">https://accounts.nintendo.com</a>轉region做日本/美國<br />\n <br />\nQ: 電量顯示有問題? 叉到100%熄機再開無左十幾%? 叉到XX%之後唔識再上?<br />\nA: Bug黎, 要等更新解決, 唔好熄機就得 (Sleep mode方便好多添啦) <br />\n <br />\nQ: JoyCon 連接有問題/ 用用下無反應?<br />\nA: 可以試下撳實JoyCon側邊個Sync掣2秒<br />\n<br />\nQ: 點揀叉電器/USB-C 線?<br />\nA: <a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/5oXEONa.png\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F5oXEONa.png&d=w1FSeGkS6ex%2B3phm3q1pv%2F7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=1bcd70ba\" target=\"_blank\">https://i.imgur.com/5oXEONa.png</a><br />\n <br />\nQ: JoyCon手帶調轉插點算?<br />\nA: <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7bfhKo7dqIo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D7bfhKo7dqIo&d=w1FSeGkS6ex%2B3phm3q1pv%2F7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=ad735fa9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7bfhKo7dqIo</a><br />\n <br />\nQ: 點連5Ghz WiFi?<br />\nA: Set 個WiFi Channel去36-64 or 100-140之間<br />\n <br />\nQ: 點連啲要打ac pw 登入嘅WIFI?<br />\nA: 無解<br />\n<br />\nQ: 部機黑畫面/定咗格/撳電源掣冇反應<br />\nA: 長撳開關掣十二秒<br />\n <br />\nQ: 要keep咩先有保養?<br />\nA: 1. 需維修的主機及配件 2. 主機外箱　 3. 印有銷售店舖名稱或蓋印之購買收據　4. 主機包裝內之香港原裝行貨保固證 <a href=\"http://www.nintendo.com.hk/switch/repair.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nintendo.com.hk%2Fswitch%2Frepair.html&d=w1FSeGkS6ex%2B3phm3q1pv%2F7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=eb7e7157\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nintendo.com.hk/switch/repair.html</a><br />\n <br />\nQ: 孖車8/Zelda咩版先有中文/英文/日文?<br />\nA: 跟你部機嘅語言(可以入設定轉)<br />\n <br />\nQ: Switch行版/日版/美版有咩分別?<br />\nA: 行版有保養同香港用嘅三腳火牛(不過任何版本都係用國際牛)，其他一樣，內置多國語言(無中文)<br />\n <br />\nQ: Switch有無鎖區?<br />\nA: 無，eShop 分區跟 ac，一機可同時登入 8 個 ac <br />\n <br />\nQ: 點解話入唔到eShop?話shop not available?<br />\nA: 港服未開，建議開多個美國/日本ac 入 美/日eShop啦<br />\n <br />\nQ: 左Joy-Con出事?<br />\nA: Joy-Con連接/同步問題解決方法:<br />\n更新Switch系統後插左右Joy-Cons落Switch本體再重開機<span style=\"color: red;\">或</span>可解決Joy-Con連接/同步問題<br />\n亦可嘗試入手掣setting disconnect joycon 再重新開機<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">都係唔得嘅可以致電香港任天堂安排測試&amp;更換</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.nintendo.com.hk/switch/repair.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nintendo.com.hk%2Fswitch%2Frepair.html&d=w1FSeGkS6ex%2B3phm3q1pv%2F7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=eb7e7157\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nintendo.com.hk/switch/repair.html</a>"},{"pid":"8ee71a8a7cf9d2d45e0065e2d32c88144a0cfe02","tid":585751,"uid":66113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T02:52:37.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>Switch</strong></span> and <span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>Play</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\"><strong>Nintendo Switch</strong></span> 2017年3月3日 於香港正式發售<br />\n售價 港幣$2,340<br />\n<em><span style=\"color: red;\">跟機國際牛，不設鎖區</span></em></span><br />\n<br />\n任天堂Switch香港官網<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.nintendo.com.hk/switch/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nintendo.com.hk%2Fswitch%2F&d=w1FSeGkS6ex%2B3phm3q1pv%2F7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=c25c3f0a\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nintendo.com.hk/switch/</a></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/t6Dbg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2Ft6Dbg.png&h=11f14dfe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n3DS Q&amp;A:<a href=\"http://docs.google.com/document/d/1iqBhGbOJ9JQRq6_fSdyYiK9JBT49KlTnMarTu_FAPZ4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1iqBhGbOJ9JQRq6_fSdyYiK9JBT49KlTnMarTu_FAPZ4&d=w1FSeGkS6ex%2B3phm3q1pv%2F7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=2ad5cc34\" target=\"_blank\">http://docs.google.com/document/d/1iqBhGbOJ9JQRq6_fSdyYiK9JBT49KlTnMarTu_FAPZ4</a><br />\nWiiU Q&amp;A:<a href=\"http://pastebin.com/a5wwpUf9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpastebin.com%2Fa5wwpUf9&d=w1FSeGkS6ex%2B3phm3q1pv%2F7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=407e81cb\" target=\"_blank\">http://pastebin.com/a5wwpUf9</a></div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">任天堂Switch Online App開放下載 (香港未有)</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DFELfwUXYAUv_l8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDFELfwUXYAUv_l8.jpg&h=467237b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nApp功能<br />\n1.同唔同遊戲會有連動要素, 例如Splatoon2, 透過個app可以睇到自己嘅對戰相關數據同買裝<br />\n2. 可以進行語音通話<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DFGMQiBUMAAJRz2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDFGMQiBUMAAJRz2.jpg&h=91a4ea8a&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">任天堂Switch會員服務2018年9月開始收費 </span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DBTWWkfWAAAbXXD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDBTWWkfWAAAbXXD.jpg&h=d41ddfcd&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\"><br />\n服務內容:<br />\n1. 網絡對戰, 直至2018年9月服務正式開始前用家可免費使用此功能<br />\n2. 使用網絡對戰開房/配對及語音通話App, 其測試版已開放下載<br />\n3. 可以遊玩<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">追加網絡功能</span></strong>的&quot;任天堂經典遊戲&quot;, 遊戲數目會不斷增加, 首批已知遊戲包括 「Super Mario Bros. 3」, 「Balloon Fight」, 「Dr. Mario」<br />\n4. eShop 遊戲優惠<br />\n5. 其他功能尚待公佈<br />\n<br />\n收費: <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">每年</span> 19.99USD/ 2400YEN (<span style=\"color: red;\">約港幣$160</span>)<br />\n可只購買1或3個月會員資格, 惟其價格亦較昂貴<br />\n</div><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Nintendo Switch家長監護程式</span></strong></span><br />\n*裝左可以睇返自已玩左幾耐<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/C8nGrvGXkAAhyFV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FC8nGrvGXkAAhyFV.jpg&h=b021040c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nAndroid:<a href=\"http://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.nintendo.znma\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcom.nintendo.znma&d=w1FSeGkS6ex%2B3phm3q1pv%2F7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=5abf81f7\" target=\"_blank\">http://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.nintendo.znma</a><br />\niOS:<a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/hk/app/id1190074407\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fitunes.apple.com%2Fhk%2Fapp%2Fid1190074407&d=w1FSeGkS6ex%2B3phm3q1pv%2F7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=c077f5f2\" target=\"_blank\">https://itunes.apple.com/hk/app/id1190074407</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">任天堂會員 - MyNintendo (對應中文)</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"http://my.nintendo.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmy.nintendo.com%2F&d=w1FSeGkS6ex%2B3phm3q1pv%2F7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=f19cf58a\" target=\"_blank\">http://my.nintendo.com/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><em><span style=\"color: red;\">3DS 舊機轉新機 <span style=\"font-size: large;\">資料轉移</span> 教學</span></em></strong><br />\n<a href=\"http://i.imag.cx/t6XVN.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2Ft6XVN.jpg&d=w1FSeGkS6ex%2B3phm3q1pv%2F7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=6e433470\" target=\"_blank\">http://i.imag.cx/t6XVN.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><em><strong>港版機/New3DS(LL)/2DS特點:</strong></em></span><br />\n<a href=\"http://i.imag.cx/t66O3.png\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2Ft66O3.png&d=w1FSeGkS6ex%2B3phm3q1pv%2F7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=e7ea14aa\" target=\"_blank\">http://i.imag.cx/t66O3.png</a><br />\n[/center]"},{"pid":"db7047e03cbe5676138cf552aef94ac28ab98072","tid":585751,"uid":66113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T02:53:19.000Z","msg":"轉去呢度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/585760/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/585760/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"87e667fbdd6d9f2ba7baa14ca202b29e6bcf803c","tid":585751,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T03:31:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}